<p>Effective Date: 30 August 2024</p>
<p>Company Name: ABC Retail</p>

<p>ABC Retailers values your privacy and is committed to protecting the personal information you share with us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your data when you interact with our online retail services.</p>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
<p>We collect and process the following types of information:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Includes your name, email address, phone number, and other contact details you provide when placing orders or communicating with us.</li>
    <li><strong>Order Information:</strong> Details of the products you purchase, order history, and transaction data.</li>
    <li><strong>Product Images:</strong> Any images you upload or that are associated with the products you purchase.</li>
    <li><strong>Technical Information:</strong> Information about your device, IP address, browser type, and usage data collected through cookies and other tracking technologies.</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>We use your information to:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Process Orders:</strong> Manage and fulfill your orders efficiently.</li>
    <li><strong>Improve Our Services:</strong> Enhance your shopping experience and improve the performance of our website.</li>
    <li><strong>Communicate with You:</strong> Respond to your inquiries, provide customer support, and send you updates related to your orders or our services.</li>
    <li><strong>Analyze Data:</strong> Understand usage patterns to optimize our services, personalize recommendations, and improve operational efficiency.</li>
    <li><strong>Ensure Security:</strong> Protect against fraudulent activities and safeguard your data.</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Data Storage and Security</h2>
<p>We utilize Azure cloud services to store and protect your information. Our data storage solutions include Azure Blob Storage for product images and Azure Queue Storage for managing messages. We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access and breaches.</p>

<h2>4. Sharing Your Information</h2>
<p>We do not sell or trade your personal information. We may share your information with:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Third parties who assist us in operating our web app and processing transactions.</li>
    <li><strong>Legal Authorities:</strong> When required by law or to protect our rights and the safety of others.</li>
</ul>

<h2>5. Your Data Protection Rights</h2>
<p>You have the following rights concerning your personal data:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Access and Update:</strong> Request access to and update your personal information.</li>
    <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request the deletion of your data, subject to legal and contractual obligations.</li>
    <li><strong>Restriction:</strong> Limit the processing of your data in certain circumstances.</li>
    <li><strong>Objection:</strong> Object to processing based on legitimate interests or for direct marketing purposes.</li>
</ul>
<p>To exercise these rights, please contact us at st10310998@vcconnect.edu.za.</p>

<h2>6. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
<p>We use cookies and similar technologies to collect information about your interactions with our website. You can manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>

